event Approval(address indexed owner, address indexed approved, uint256 indexed tokenId)
event ApprovalForAll(address indexed owner, address indexed operator, bool approved)
event DelegateChanged(address indexed delegator, address indexed fromDelegate, address indexed toDelegate)
event DelegateVotesChanged(address indexed delegate, uint256 oldBalance, uint256 newBalance)
event DropCompleted(uint256 indexed dropId, uint256 endTime)
event DropCreated(uint256 indexed dropId, uint256 startIndex, uint256 dropSize, uint256 startTime, string dropHash)
event DropDelegate(address delegator, address delegatee, uint256 tokenId)
event Transfer(address indexed from, address indexed to, uint256 indexed tokenId)
function checkpoints(address, uint256) view returns (uint32 fromBlock, uint32 votes)
function delegateBySig(address delegator, address delegatee, uint256 expiry, uint8 v, bytes32 r, bytes32 s)
function drop() view returns (uint256 endIndex, bool initiated, uint256 endTime)
function getPriorVotes(address voter, uint256 blockNumber) view returns (uint32)
function isApprovedForAll(address owner, address operator) view returns (bool)
function safeTransferFrom(address from, address to, uint256 id)
function safeTransferFrom(address from, address to, uint256 id, bytes data)
function transferFrom(address from, address to, uint256 id)
